  ${
    $d x y $.
    $( ` ZZ ` is a commutative ring.  (Contributed by FL, 18-Apr-2010.) $)
    zintdom $p |- <. + , x. >. e. ( RingOps i^i Com2 ) $=
      ( vx vy caddc cmul crngo ccm2 cin wcel cv co wceq wral cc wi eqcoms ax-mp
      cdm 3syl eleq2i cvv cop elin crn cxp wfo cabl cnaddablo cgr cmnd ablogrpo
      cnrngo grpomnd cmagm cexid mndmgmid ax-addopr fdm dmeq dmxpid eqtr expcom
